  "content": "<h2>背景</h2><p data-pid=\"OvFUGpnB\">前置知识，介绍了 Anki 卡片的生成原理：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/453004176/answer/1845486966\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-92248978e5dab5364c2c5cd146155aa5_120x160.jpg\" data-image-width=\"398\" data-image-height=\"656\" class=\"internal\">Anki 提示空白卡片，但打开编辑，所有内容都有，这个是什么原因呀？</a><p data-pid=\"W21roM3k\">看完这个介绍就能明白，Anki 的卡片是通过笔记+模板的方式生成的。题主是想将一条笔记对应的两张卡片中的一张改为填空题，想要做到这点，必须要修改模板：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e4de0bc90cd3c532f27f871cbb333a00_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"555\" data-rawheight=\"272\" data-original-token=\"v2-e4de0bc90cd3c532f27f871cbb333a00\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e4fa0bc86dd24f60f15c6df0a498c1ce_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"555\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e4de0bc90cd3c532f27f871cbb333a00_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;555&#39; height=&#39;272&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"555\" data-rawheight=\"272\" data-original-token=\"v2-e4de0bc90cd3c532f27f871cbb333a00\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e4fa0bc86dd24f60f15c6df0a498c1ce_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"555\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e4de0bc90cd3c532f27f871cbb333a00_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e4de0bc90cd3c532f27f871cbb333a00_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f6f8d6e644b870de513c12b47dc140ff_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"522\" data-rawheight=\"392\" data-original-token=\"v2-f6f8d6e644b870de513c12b47dc140ff\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9d4039015e16e44961f05b4cef15eb56_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"522\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f6f8d6e644b870de513c12b47dc140ff_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;522&#39; height=&#39;392&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"522\" data-rawheight=\"392\" data-original-token=\"v2-f6f8d6e644b870de513c12b47dc140ff\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9d4039015e16e44961f05b4cef15eb56_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"522\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f6f8d6e644b870de513c12b47dc140ff_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f6f8d6e644b870de513c12b47dc140ff_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b290a1311c16d7ee7d2ec70bfe542492_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"238\" data-original-token=\"v2-b290a1311c16d7ee7d2ec70bfe542492\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d2ea2e3e67b5a4b25c256e1eb633f264_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"360\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;360&#39; height=&#39;238&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"238\" data-original-token=\"v2-b290a1311c16d7ee7d2ec70bfe542492\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d2ea2e3e67b5a4b25c256e1eb633f264_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"360\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b290a1311c16d7ee7d2ec70bfe542492_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"AQkrKJKt\">假设 front 是英文，back 是中文。</p><p data-pid=\"O82YL0IZ\">题主实际上就是想把这个模板中的 back -&gt; front 改成可以输入答案的形式，那么参考我以前的一篇回答就行了：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/372880799/answer/1054955943\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-443a5006b9a92e0543a34b0a7e682990_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1680\" data-image-height=\"1050\" class=\"internal\">Anki的填空题怎么输入？</a><h2>教程</h2><p data-pid=\"pYfhKc65\">当然，这个回答是针对填空题的，我这些讲一下问答题怎么操作：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-176449737ab7338ee27397e664d16736_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1135\" data-rawheight=\"702\" data-original-token=\"v2-176449737ab7338ee27397e664d16736\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8c4bf7bd4859ad2369b80d2f72779b03_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1135\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-176449737ab7338ee27397e664d16736_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1135&#39; height=&#39;702&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1135\" data-rawheight=\"702\" data-original-token=\"v2-176449737ab7338ee27397e664d16736\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8c4bf7bd4859ad2369b80d2f72779b03_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1135\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-176449737ab7338ee27397e664d16736_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-176449737ab7338ee27397e664d16736_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"7pyrRAYC\">回到刚才的 basic and reversed card，切到 back -&gt; front 的正面模板，在 {{Back}} 下面添加 {{type:Front}} 即可。</p><h2>效果</h2><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b7f3ddd127b75558ee5b69aca141aa5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"661\" data-rawheight=\"519\" data-original-token=\"v2-8b7f3ddd127b75558ee5b69aca141aa5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-35dfb80815ab02a1d7b51dfd5fbe88c8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"661\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8b7f3ddd127b75558ee5b69aca141aa5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;661&#39; height=&#39;519&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"661\" data-rawheight=\"519\" data-original-token=\"v2-8b7f3ddd127b75558ee5b69aca141aa5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-35dfb80815ab02a1d7b51dfd5fbe88c8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"661\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8b7f3ddd127b75558ee5b69aca141aa5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b7f3ddd127b75558ee5b69aca141aa5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4c381f323c2790c419373ce0148d077_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"659\" data-rawheight=\"521\" data-original-token=\"v2-b4c381f323c2790c419373ce0148d077\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a1971fbde651c704f3aabf1764c3caa_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"659\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b4c381f323c2790c419373ce0148d077_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;659&#39; height=&#39;521&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"659\" data-rawheight=\"521\" data-original-token=\"v2-b4c381f323c2790c419373ce0148d077\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a1971fbde651c704f3aabf1764c3caa_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"659\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b4c381f323c2790c419373ce0148d077_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4c381f323c2790c419373ce0148d077_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"pvQPnLx7\">成功！</p><p data-pid=\"-pHo4Fr8\">更多 Anki 相关的教程，请见：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-acfa8f607f2d3c74ba5c660c3ab25df0_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1161\" data-image-height=\"500\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：Anki 教程(电子书)与 B 站 Ankidroid 教程(视频)快速通道</a><p></p>",
